204
00:14:55.120 --> 00:14:57.000
To break this deadlock,

205
00:14:57.000 --> 00:15:02.420
His Awesomeness, Queen,
has entrusted me with a secret weapon.

206
00:15:06.010 --> 00:15:09.100
Looking hot as ever, Madam Speed!

207
00:15:09.100 --> 00:15:11.350
So, where is this "secret weapon"?

208
00:15:12.720 --> 00:15:13.890
Right here.

209
00:15:14.690 --> 00:15:18.400
It'll dramatically boost your body's healing,

210
00:15:18.400 --> 00:15:22.320
and improve muscle strength...

211
00:15:23.070 --> 00:15:24.450
significantly!

212
00:15:24.450 --> 00:15:25.570
What?!

213
00:15:25.570 --> 00:15:26.860
Are you for real?!

214
00:15:27.450 --> 00:15:28.740
That said...

215
00:15:28.740 --> 00:15:31.580
it looks really delicious...

216
00:15:34.830 --> 00:15:38.460
Give me that dumpling immediately!

217
00:15:38.460 --> 00:15:40.790
Headliner Briscola
Gorilla Smile Fruit
Beast Pirates

218
00:15:40.790 --> 00:15:44.470
Looks like you got pretty roughed up, Briscola.

219
00:15:44.470 --> 00:15:45.470
Shut up!

220
00:15:45.840 --> 00:15:50.220
If I don't get my revenge against
those annoying, shitty Straw Hats,

221
00:15:50.220 --> 00:15:54.180
I'll never be satisfied!

222
00:15:58.020 --> 00:16:00.150
I'll let you have one, then.

223
00:16:00.150 --> 00:16:02.770
Just one bite will flip your world upside down.

224
00:16:04.030 --> 00:16:05.030
Here.

225
00:16:08.530 --> 00:16:10.740
How is it, Briscola?

226
00:16:12.780 --> 00:16:15.410
Feels like it's working...

227
00:16:15.410 --> 00:16:18.250
Or maybe not...

228
00:16:18.250 --> 00:16:20.130
No way.

229
00:16:20.130 --> 00:16:20.670
Huh?

230
00:16:20.670 --> 00:16:22.340
You fool...

231
00:16:22.340 --> 00:16:27.470
You're not trying to say that
Queen's homemade dumpling...

232
00:16:27.930 --> 00:16:33.680
is a failure, are you?

233
00:16:33.680 --> 00:16:35.060
Gulp!

234
00:16:37.020 --> 00:16:38.020
Boing!

235
00:16:38.020 --> 00:16:40.270
Boing! Boing! Boing!

236
00:16:40.270 --> 00:16:41.770
Wee!

237
00:16:43.440 --> 00:16:45.940
It's amazing!

238
00:16:47.320 --> 00:16:50.990
I feel pure power coursing through my veins!

239
00:16:54.240 --> 00:16:55.740
That's awesome!

240
00:16:55.740 --> 00:16:58.210
I want one too, Boss Briscola!

241
00:17:00.710 --> 00:17:04.210
Madam Speed! Might I have a dumpling too?

242
00:17:04.210 --> 00:17:05.420
I want one too!

243
00:17:05.420 --> 00:17:06.630
– Two for us!
– Two for us!

244
00:17:07.050 --> 00:17:08.630
Of course!

245
00:17:09.380 --> 00:17:13.010
I've got enough here for every last Gifter!

246
00:17:13.010 --> 00:17:14.930
– Yay!
– Yay!

247
00:17:19.770 --> 00:17:21.850
– Delicious!
– Delicious!

248
00:17:21.850 --> 00:17:24.900
Once you finish eating, get ready to fight!

249
00:17:24.900 --> 00:17:26.650
There's no time to waste!

250
00:17:26.650 --> 00:17:30.610
The Straw Hats won't wait for us!

251
00:17:36.240 --> 00:17:37.660
Horsella!

252
00:17:37.660 --> 00:17:42.210
I wanna go to Onigashima, too!

253
00:17:42.210 --> 00:17:47.210
No one let me go with them...

254
00:17:47.670 --> 00:17:48.880
So...

255
00:17:51.340 --> 00:17:53.890
Leave it to me, Master!

256
00:17:59.680 --> 00:18:01.940
Millet Dumpling!

257
00:18:02.600 --> 00:18:06.190
Every one of these brings us another ally!

258
00:18:10.610 --> 00:18:13.530
Millet Dumpling...

259
00:18:14.030 --> 00:18:17.080
Millet Dumpling!

260
00:18:24.040 --> 00:18:26.080
Millet Dump–

261
00:18:28.380 --> 00:18:32.050
Master, I think you'd better stop now...

262
00:18:33.470 --> 00:18:36.510
I'm okay...

263
00:18:36.970 --> 00:18:42.390
There's no way I can
bring Kaido down all by myself...

264
00:18:43.310 --> 00:18:44.350
So...

265
00:18:44.350 --> 00:18:47.770
I have to do whatever I can to help!

266
00:18:48.150 --> 00:18:52.400
I want a Wano without Orochi and Kaido,
with Momo as the shogun!

267
00:18:52.400 --> 00:18:54.240
That's the future I want to see!

268
00:18:57.490 --> 00:19:01.950
And I'm tired of being hungry all the time...

269
00:19:01.950 --> 00:19:04.410
I wanna eat...

270
00:19:06.040 --> 00:19:07.000
I understand.

271
00:19:07.000 --> 00:19:08.630
Let's fight!

272
00:19:08.630 --> 00:19:10.300
Yeah, let's do it!

273
00:19:10.670 --> 00:19:15.090
Let's have something to eat first, and then
we'll lie in wait for our chance to strike!

274
00:19:15.090 --> 00:19:16.590
– Okay!
– All right!

275
00:19:19.430 --> 00:19:21.310
Ready...

276
00:19:21.310 --> 00:19:22.770
Start!

277
00:19:25.770 --> 00:19:26.350
Eat this!

278
00:19:28.520 --> 00:19:29.980
Huh?! It's delicious!

279
00:19:30.900 --> 00:19:31.650
Eat this!

280
00:19:34.070 --> 00:19:35.110
– Delicious!
– Delicious!

281
00:19:35.110 --> 00:19:35.900
Eat this!

282
00:19:35.900 --> 00:19:36.610
Delicious!

283
00:19:36.610 --> 00:19:37.160
Eat this!

284
00:19:37.160 --> 00:19:37.950
Delicious!

285
00:19:37.950 --> 00:19:38.490
Eat this!

286
00:19:38.490 --> 00:19:39.830
Delicious!

287
00:19:39.830 --> 00:19:42.450
Eat up, Gifters!

288
00:19:45.410 --> 00:19:49.540
Look! It's the vice warden
from Udon, Daifugo!

289
00:19:49.540 --> 00:19:50.670
Take him down!

290
00:19:50.670 --> 00:19:53.710
You put us through hell!

291
00:19:53.710 --> 00:19:57.720
Sorry about that, guys!
Let's just put it aside for a bit!

292
00:19:57.720 --> 00:19:58.470
What?!

293
00:20:01.300 --> 00:20:04.770
– Oh, Daifugo, sir! Thank you for your hard work!
– Oh, Daifugo, sir! Thank you for your hard work!

294
00:20:04.770 --> 00:20:07.190
No time for pleasantries!

295
00:20:07.190 --> 00:20:08.600
Eat this!

296
00:20:08.600 --> 00:20:09.860
Eat this!

297
00:20:09.860 --> 00:20:11.360
Eat this!

298
00:20:12.190 --> 00:20:16.530
Eat this! Serve the master!

299
00:20:22.080 --> 00:20:25.450
General Left!

300
00:20:43.850 --> 00:20:45.770
We're not done yet!

301
00:20:52.060 --> 00:20:53.570
Sasaki, sir!

302
00:21:00.320 --> 00:21:02.320
This is it!

303
00:21:02.320 --> 00:21:03.780
General–

304
00:21:05.490 --> 00:21:08.710
Hold him down!

305
00:21:14.540 --> 00:21:15.750
Hey, come on!

306
00:21:15.750 --> 00:21:18.010
Outta the way, you bums!

307
00:21:19.590 --> 00:21:25.060
You may be strong, but even you
can't shake off this many of us!

308
00:21:25.060 --> 00:21:29.350
Didn't you know? We Gifters
have been given special abilities!

309
00:21:29.350 --> 00:21:31.190
We're no ordinary soldiers!

310
00:21:35.230 --> 00:21:37.820
These are some real tough customers...

311
00:21:44.240 --> 00:21:46.790
– Franky!
– Franky!

312
00:21:47.160 --> 00:21:48.410
That must be...

313
00:21:48.410 --> 00:21:52.000
Usopp! Nami! And Otama!

314
00:21:52.000 --> 00:21:53.120
Wha... why?!

315
00:21:53.120 --> 00:21:56.800
Wait, this is no time for questions!

316
00:21:56.800 --> 00:21:59.880
Good timing! Help me get these guys off of–

317
00:22:07.180 --> 00:22:11.020
– Help!
– Help!

318
00:22:13.440 --> 00:22:15.980
They're being chased by
everyone and their mother!

319
00:22:16.480 --> 00:22:21.150
For crying out loud!
Things just went from bad to worse!

320
00:22:21.150 --> 00:22:24.700
Gifters! Push ahead and block the way!

321
00:22:25.280 --> 00:22:27.910
When it comes to numbers,
we have the advantage!

322
00:22:27.910 --> 00:22:32.660
They can't win unless
the tide turns all over the island!

323
00:22:32.660 --> 00:22:35.330
What am I supposed to do?!

324
00:22:37.210 --> 00:22:38.000
I...

325
00:22:38.710 --> 00:22:43.380
I'm here to turn that tide!

326
00:22:48.760 --> 00:22:50.890
Everyone, please!

327
00:22:51.470 --> 00:22:53.020
Franosuke needs you!

328
00:22:53.020 --> 00:22:56.940
Help him!

329
00:22:58.360 --> 00:23:02.110
– Got it, Master!
– Got it, Master!

330
00:23:02.110 --> 00:23:03.030
What?!

331
00:23:10.450 --> 00:23:11.330
Alright!

332
00:23:16.670 --> 00:23:19.710
Whew! That was close!

333
00:23:21.630 --> 00:23:23.670
Great work, guys!

334
00:23:26.800 --> 00:23:30.060
What the hell are you dolts thinking?!

335
00:23:30.060 --> 00:23:31.220
Sasaki!

336
00:23:32.430 --> 00:23:34.680
Page One! Ulti!

337
00:23:34.680 --> 00:23:38.560
They've switched sides! Trample them all!

338
00:23:38.560 --> 00:23:40.730
Switched sides?!

339
00:23:40.730 --> 00:23:44.900
What could they possibly gain
by siding with the samurai?

340
00:23:44.900 --> 00:23:47.660
It's probably one of their abilities!

341
00:23:47.990 --> 00:23:49.820
Isn't that right?!

342
00:23:50.280 --> 00:23:53.370
You really are asking for
a crushed skull this time!

343
00:23:53.370 --> 00:23:55.000
Not again!

344
00:23:55.330 --> 00:23:56.500
Lightning alert!

345
00:23:58.080 --> 00:24:01.840
This one's a real
heart-stopper, so look alive!

346
00:24:01.840 --> 00:24:04.130
Thunder Lance...

347
00:24:04.130 --> 00:24:05.550
Tempo!

348
00:24:07.840 --> 00:24:08.930
Big Sis!

349
00:24:13.430 --> 00:24:16.020
Damn! That hurts!

350
00:24:16.020 --> 00:24:18.980
She's done it now! That rotten bitch!

351
00:24:22.230 --> 00:24:26.900
I knew that wouldn't be enough...
I need more powerful lightning!

352
00:24:26.900 --> 00:24:29.780
She used some weird trick!

353
00:24:29.780 --> 00:24:32.580
Guys! Take them down!

354
00:24:32.580 --> 00:24:34.870
They'll only get in our way if we leave them be!

355
00:24:34.870 --> 00:24:36.910
– Aye, aye, Sasaki!
– Aye, aye, Sasaki!

356
00:24:36.910 --> 00:24:38.330
Not on my watch!

357
00:24:38.330 --> 00:24:39.040
Lethal...

358
00:24:39.040 --> 00:24:40.250
Millet Dumpling Star!

359
00:24:40.250 --> 00:24:41.170
Millet Dumpling Star!

360
00:24:41.170 --> 00:24:42.250
Millet Dumpling Star!

361
00:24:42.250 --> 00:24:43.500
Millet Dumpling Star!

362
00:24:44.750 --> 00:24:46.800
What was that?

363
00:24:46.800 --> 00:24:48.260
Everybody!

364
00:24:48.930 --> 00:24:51.760
Follow me!

365
00:24:56.520 --> 00:24:59.140
– Aye, aye, Master!
– Aye, aye, Master!

366
00:25:03.440 --> 00:25:05.280
Huh?!

367
00:25:05.280 --> 00:25:08.320
What?! Hey! What's going on?!

368
00:25:08.320 --> 00:25:10.160
Wait, Armored Division!

369
00:25:10.160 --> 00:25:12.200
Whoa there.

370
00:25:13.070 --> 00:25:15.700
You oughta stay focused.

371
00:25:15.700 --> 00:25:17.410
Did you forget...

372
00:25:24.960 --> 00:25:26.920
who you're fighting?

373
00:25:28.760 --> 00:25:30.680
Franken-Sword...

374
00:25:37.850 --> 00:25:44.400
V-for-Victory Flash!

375
00:25:56.660 --> 00:25:57.370
Damn...

376
00:25:59.370 --> 00:26:02.670
Wh-What the hell is this?!

377
00:26:03.880 --> 00:26:06.170
Be a good boy.

378
00:26:06.170 --> 00:26:08.710
Black Leg Sanji.

379
00:26:06.210 --> 00:26:08.710
Banquet Hall

Third Floor

380
00:26:10.510 --> 00:26:11.630
My goodness...

381
00:26:12.180 --> 00:26:15.010
Such a cute boy, acting out like this.

382
00:26:16.100 --> 00:26:18.970
So much power, but what a shame...

383
00:26:19.430 --> 00:26:22.940
You beat the hell out of the men,

384
00:26:22.940 --> 00:26:26.610
but you can't even lay a finger on the women.

385
00:26:26.610 --> 00:26:30.110
It seems your chances of victory
have dropped to zero.

386
00:26:30.650 --> 00:26:34.490
Your life is in the palm of my hand.

387
00:26:35.490 --> 00:26:38.030
Now then, it's time for you to call out...

388
00:26:38.030 --> 00:26:40.040
for Nico Robin!

389
00:26:42.620 --> 00:26:44.670
This is Caiman Lady.

390
00:26:49.670 --> 00:26:51.920
If you speak loudly to this woman...

391
00:26:52.380 --> 00:26:54.840
your voice will be heard all over the castle.

392
00:26:55.680 --> 00:26:58.430
After that, I'll set you free.

393
00:26:58.970 --> 00:27:01.890
Those were Kaido's orders.

394
00:27:02.890 --> 00:27:06.480
What are you gonna do to Robin?

395
00:27:07.860 --> 00:27:09.520
Let's see...

396
00:27:09.520 --> 00:27:12.570
We'll gang up on her, capture her...

397
00:27:12.570 --> 00:27:16.160
and maim her limbs until she's paralyzed.

398
00:27:16.870 --> 00:27:20.910
Only once we're "finished" with her,
which could take years and years,

399
00:27:21.260 --> 00:27:23.080
will we finally kill her.

400
00:27:23.080 --> 00:27:24.660
So don't you worry.

401
00:27:29.000 --> 00:27:30.670
Damn you...

402
00:27:30.670 --> 00:27:33.170
Don't underestimate Nico Robin!

403
00:27:34.050 --> 00:27:36.470
Detected! Detected!

404
00:27:34.090 --> 00:27:36.470
Performance Floor

405
00:27:36.470 --> 00:27:41.010
Red Scabbard samurai, detected!

406
00:27:45.520 --> 00:27:50.230
It seems they've escaped the rooftop battle!

407
00:27:50.230 --> 00:27:52.900
Bloodied and beaten!

408
00:27:55.030 --> 00:28:00.490
But still breathing, it seems!

409
00:28:00.490 --> 00:28:03.910
Location... behind the castle tower!

410
00:28:03.910 --> 00:28:07.790
The second floor of the treasury
at the second bailey!

411
00:28:08.290 --> 00:28:10.540
They must've escaped from Kaido.

412
00:28:10.540 --> 00:28:12.500
I've got my hands full over here.

413
00:28:12.500 --> 00:28:14.210
Can someone else handle it?

414
00:28:14.710 --> 00:28:18.640
Go to the treasury right away
and kill all the samurai!

415
00:28:18.640 --> 00:28:19.760
Go to the treasury right away
and kill all the samurai!

416
00:28:19.760 --> 00:28:22.850
Did you get all of that, Madame Black Maria?

417
00:28:22.850 --> 00:28:25.480
Yes, King...

418
00:28:25.480 --> 00:28:27.640
I'll go.

419
00:28:27.640 --> 00:28:31.650
This floor is connected to
the second floor of the treasury.

420
00:28:32.230 --> 00:28:35.110
Want me to finish the Red Scabbards off?

421
00:28:35.110 --> 00:28:37.030
Yeah, thanks!

422
00:28:37.030 --> 00:28:40.370
Kin'emon... They all lost?!

423
00:28:40.370 --> 00:28:41.570
Wait! Don't go!

424
00:28:41.570 --> 00:28:44.870
But be careful! There are ten people...

425
00:28:45.910 --> 00:28:46.790
in that room!

426
00:28:46.790 --> 00:28:50.420
It's hard to make out in the darkness,

427
00:28:50.420 --> 00:28:55.670
but someone is trying to help the samurai!

428
00:28:55.670 --> 00:28:57.630
Hurry up and kill them!

429
00:28:58.260 --> 00:28:59.630
Someone's...

430
00:29:00.010 --> 00:29:01.680
in there!
